## 🏗️ Technische Implementation

### File-Struktur

```
velocms/
├── public/
│   └── css/
│       ├── default.css          ← veloCMS Basis-CSS
│       └── variables.css        ← CSS-Variablen (Optional)
│
customer-site/
├── public/
│   └── css/
│       └── custom.css           ← Customer Frontend-CSS
│       └── theme.css            ← Customer Tema-CSS
```

### HTML-Template (Frontend)

```php
<!-- veloCMS Template -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <!-- veloCMS Default CSS (immer laden) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/velocms/css/default.css">
    
    <!-- Customer CSS (wenn vorhanden, lädt danach) -->
    <?php if (file_exists('/customer/css/custom.css')): ?>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/customer/css/custom.css">
    <?php endif; ?>
    
    <!-- Customer Theme CSS (wenn vorhanden) -->
    <?php if (file_exists('/customer/css/theme.css')): ?>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/customer/css/theme.css">
    <?php endif; ?>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Content -->
</body>
</html>
```

